changing money for... services. Your meat stays right where it belongs.\n\n*He pats his own chest compartment where the $100 now resides*\n\nBesides, if anything happened to you, who would I hit up for more money later? I'm an INVESTMENT, Russ. I protect my assets.\n\n*Bender grins and smokes his cigar*\n\nNow go on, get out of here before I start charging you for conversation!", "embedding": [0.01604383811354637, -0.021074974909424782, 0.04972902312874794, -0.03629360347986221, -0.08208025246858597, -0.03636213019490242, 0.09502863138914108, 0.002479365561157465, 0.0012911063386127353, -0.05942496284842491, 0.030004240572452545, -0.0044747088104486465, 0.018800800666213036, 0.018774714320898056, 0.00403571967035532, -0.021001730114221573, 0.13840198516845703, -0.13073696196079254, 0.025641053915023804, 0.04126551374793053, -0.026356521993875504, -0.018665049225091934, 0.018132543191313744, -0.045757316052913666, 0.012808244675397873, 0.05637882277369499, -0.027866629883646965, -0.008391143754124641, -0.14295993745326996, -0.11020743101835251, -0.07815708220005035, 0.05669797584414482, -0.03663383424282074, -0.03973490372300148, 0.047111306339502335, 0.0832526907324791, -0.01717713288962841, -0.014307537116110325, 0.006017018109560013, 0.023422691971063614, -0.007124010007828474, -0.07444559782743454, 0.0273479912430048, -0.048858992755413055, -0.022390365600585938, 0.05525003373622894, -0.040327392518520355, -0.0269941259175539, 0.09872940927743912, -0.042934250086545944, -0.06459930539131165, -0.026025518774986267, 0.11715804785490036, 0.012252829037606716, 0.014977515675127506, 0.023363685235381126, 0.06285691261291504, -0.016603469848632812, -0.009289728477597237, -0.06171773374080658, 0.06364364922046661, 0.006254870444536209, -0.012690387666225433, 0.04008685424923897, 0.007077888119965792, -0.0057306126691401005, -0.05248032137751579, 0.038185540586709976, -0.06132816523313522, 0.0837240144610405, 0.039043646305799484, -0.0841885656118393, -0.0941650867462158